						<div class="postbody">Simple, I know radius and angle.<br /><br />I want to obtain X and Y positions<br /><br />In real life, I would simply use sinus for the first unknown, then pythagore for the second one.<br /><br />However I don't have a sin function neither a square root function.<br /><br />I wouldn't want to enter values by hand in an array...<br /><br />is there a better way?</div>

